</h3><p class="sc-cZMNgc hqfPHB pf-51_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">To align with the BoE's regulations and policies, businesses and financial institutions should adhere to the following best practices:



























</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-bQtKYq czWvgn pf-53_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-54_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regular monitoring and reporting </strong>- Maintain rigorous monitoring of financial activities and regular reporting to comply with PRA guidelines.






</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-56_ pf-text-1"><strong>Risk management frameworks</strong> - Implement robust risk management frameworks to mitigate potential financial risks and ensure stability.











